# menu.db вҖ” Menu definition for flu.sh v1.1
# Format: Category|Subcategory|Label|action_id
# Lines starting with # are comments. Empty lines are ignored.
# Action IDs map 1:1 to module script filenames in modules/<action_id>.sh

# в”Җв”Җ рҹ”Қ Diagnostics в”Җв”Җ
Diagnostics|System|рҹ”Қ Status Check|status_check
Diagnostics|System|рҹ”„ Compare With Latest|status_check_compare
Diagnostics|Updates|в¬ҶпёҸ Upgrade All Tools|upgrade_all

